msgid ""
"Don't forget to change its mode to \"CanvasItem\" (if you are using a "
"Sprite):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/tutorials/plugins/editor/visual_shader_plugins.rst:30
msgid ""
"Create a script which derives from :ref:`class_VisualShaderNodeCustom`. "
"This is all you need to initialize your plugin."
msgstr ""

